body:
I get that Kayle not being clad in armor makes a lot of you upset but quick question. How many of you actually play Kayle enough to have a true opinion on her looks? Like I don't mean you played her on ARAM after rerolling twice I mean as in you have her in your top 3 champions played and besides I see something similar to how Aether WIng Kayle looks plus it could have been a whole lot worse.
 As for everyone complaining about the looks of Kayle can yall at least wait until after the character's lines,lore,moveset,and interactions come out to declare something a failure of design. I mean jesus f#@$ing christ she's not even on PBE yet. Same on yall for being shallow if someone's appearance is enough for you to not play them though considering the champion involved it doesn't matter anyways since none of you play her in her current form,s#!%, and I'm one of the first people to say f#@$ you to Riot but it tends to be for a good enough reason rather than just how someone looks. Seriously what the hell it's not even on pbe yet and yall wanna Riot about this. Worse part is you guys are so predictable that I know you all are gonna down vote this thread because it doesn't fit your opinions.
{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}}
